## Global docroot
  DocumentRoot "<%= @docroot %>"

## Directories, there should at least be a declaration for <%= @docroot %>

  <Directory "<%= @docroot %>">
    Options <%= @options %>
    AllowOverride All
<%- if @apache_version == '2.4' -%>
    Require all granted
<%- else -%>
    Order allow,deny
    allow from all
<%- end -%>
    DirectoryIndex <%= @directoryindex %>
  </Directory>
